title: Arnette Mad Decent Block Party Ambassador
description:
Apply to be an Arnette Block Party Ambassador Here: http://Live.Arnette.com

Summer music festivals are often the highlight of anyone's summer, and now Arnette is sending two lucky ambassadors on tour with Diplo and the Mad Decent Block Party all summer! If you think you've got the skills to interview DJs, become a social media guru, and do it all while seeing the country, visit live.arnette.com and apply today!
